data.description: This stunning home features 4 huge bedrooms and 3 bathrooms in 2,714 sq ft of open concept living. Beautiful en suite to the main floor master bedroom with a classic claw foot tub. Enjoy the 3 covered decks or relax at the fire pit area in the beautifully landscaped backyard. Easy entertaining in the giant kitchen fully equipped with stainless steel appliances and an island overlooking the main living space. Come take a look today!
data.whatILove: A spacious homey feeling with a constant view of treetops and the sound of singing birds.   All the necessities and comforts for living are located on the main floor while the lower level offers abundant space for guests and additional storage.
